    "discriminators": [
     "An isolated crack/crumble: broadband, unpitched fracture noise - brighter and noisier than ROCKS-IMPACT (higher spectral_flatness, more mid/HF grit) but still with NO ring. Nothing in rock sustains.",
     "Against GLASS-BREAK and CERAMICS-BREAK: no bright tinkling shard tail, far lower centroid, far lower high_band_energy.",
     "Against ROCKS-CRASH & DEBRIS: singular and front-loaded; CRASH is a collapse/slide with dozens of onsets over seconds."
    ],
