     "Against ROCKS-IMPACT: onset count is the axis - a slide is not a hit.",
     "Against DIRT & SAND-CRASH & DEBRIS: rocks are discrete and thuddy (resolvable onsets, low centroid); dirt and sand is a continuous granular hiss with unresolvable micro-onsets and much higher spectral_flatness.",
